    public static enum MethodDelegationBinder.ParameterBinding.Illegal
extends Enum<MethodDelegationBinder.ParameterBinding.Illegal>
implements MethodDelegationBinder.ParameterBinding<Void>
    A singleton representation of an illegal binding for a method parameter. An illegal binding usually suggests that a source method cannot be bound to a specific target method.
